00:26:19,720 --> 00:26:21,560
and "depressingly accurate."

423
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:24,920
The Oregonian raves:
"Who needs a drink ?"

424
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:26,880
Four reporters.

425
00:26:27,840 --> 00:26:30,320
Actually, I'm taking a buyout.

426
00:26:30,760 --> 00:26:32,040
Three reporters.

427
00:26:32,280 --> 00:26:35,840
I'm not a reporter, I'm the Director
of Social Media Strategies,

428
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:38,520
but I'm an
important part of the editorial.

429
00:26:38,600 --> 00:26:39,840
Two reporters.

430
00:26:40,080 --> 00:26:45,280
I'm also leaving. I'm being replaced
by whatever the fuck this is.

